   <concept id="DFARS_252.237-7008" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3">
      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">252.237-7008</ph> Group Interment.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause">
         <p>As prescribed in 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="DFARS-237.7003" href="237.7003.dita#DFARS_237.7003">237.7003</xref>
            (a) and (a)(6), use the following clause:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps">GROUP INTERMENT (DEC 1991)</p>
         <p>The Government will pay the Contractor for supplies and services provided for remains interred as a group on the basis of the number of caskets furnished, rather than on the basis of the number of persons in the group.</p>
         <p outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
